            "size": "h4",
            "font": "sans"
          }
        },
        "para_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>TGLab is where brands connect with the team behind TRENDYGOLF. Built as a platform for discovery and collaboration, TGLab invites emerging and established brands to introduce their products to our buying team and explore opportunities to be featured on our site.</p>"
          }
        },
        "para_2": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At TRENDYGOLF, we’re always looking for brands that push golf style and performance forward. From technical apparel and premium footwear to accessories and lifestyle products, we’re interested in partnering with brands that share our passion for modern golf culture, quality design and forward-thinking innovation.</p>"
          }
        },
        "para_3": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Through TGLab, brands can start a conversation with our buyers, showcase their collections and discuss potential retail partnerships. Whether you’re launching something new or expanding into the premium golf market, TGLabs is your gateway to joining the curated selection of brands featured at TRENDYGOLF and reaching a global community of style-conscious golfers.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
